{
  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-4592b2440620",
  "content": "## Task 6: CLI Updates — Init Modes, Rebuild, Updated Commands\n\n### Step 1: Update command definitions\n\nAdd `--full` to Init, add Rebuild command:\n\n```rust\n#[derive(Subcommand)]\nenum Commands {\n    /// Initialize Corvia (LiteStore by default, --full for SurrealDB+vLLM)\n    Init {\n        /// Use FullStore: SurrealDB + vLLM (requires Docker)\n        #[arg(long)]\n        full: bool,\n    },\n\n    /// Start the REST API server\n    Serve,\n\n    /// Ingest a Git repository\n    Ingest {\n        path: String,\n    },\n\n    /// Search ingested knowledge\n    Search {\n        query: String,\n        #[arg(short, long, default_value = \"5\")]\n        limit: usize,\n    },\n\n    /// Show status of Corvia services\n    Status,\n\n    /// Run Introspect: self-ingest + self-query validation\n    Test {\n        #[arg(long)]\n        check_only: bool,\n        #[arg(long)]\n        keep: bool,\n        #[arg(long)]\n        ci: bool,\n    },\n\n    /// Interactive demo: ingest Corvia's own code, then search it\n    Demo {\n        #[arg(long)]\n        keep: bool,\n    },\n\n    /// Rebuild LiteStore indexes from knowledge files\n    Rebuild,\n}\n```\n\n\n### Step 2: Update main() match\n\n```rust\nmatch cli.command {\n    Commands::Init { full } => cmd_init(full).await?,\n    Commands::Serve => cmd_serve().await?,\n    Commands::Ingest { path } => cmd_ingest(&path).await?,\n    Commands::Search { query, limit } => cmd_search(&query, limit).await?,\n    Commands::Status => cmd_status().await?,\n    Commands::Test { check_only, keep, ci } => cmd_test(check_only, keep, ci).await?,\n    Commands::Demo { keep } => cmd_demo(keep).await?,\n    Commands::Rebuild => cmd_rebuild().await?,\n}\n```\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-01-m1.2-litestore.md",
